Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech emotion recognition and natural language processing techniques. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper uses speech corpora to test their algorithms. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper aims to estimate the level of conversational engagement between users of a voice communication system. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques such as SVM and HMM. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with the development of algorithms for speech emotion recognition and engagement estimation.
